  "text": "The Kubernetes scheduler's ScoreExtensions interface and its accessor method ScoreExtensions() appear in 19 files across the codebase. The interface is defined in pkg/scheduler/framework/interface.go (lines 597-603) as part of the Score plugin extension system. The ScorePlugin interface in the same file (lines 605-616) declares the ScoreExtensions() method that returns a ScoreExtensions interface or nil.\n\nEight plugin implementations under pkg/scheduler/framework/plugins/ implement the ScoreExtensions() method: Fit (noderesources/fit.go:99), InterPodAffinity (interpodaffinity/scoring.go:300), PodTopologySpread (podtopologyspread/scoring.go:269), NodeAffinity (nodeaffinity/node_affinity.go:300), VolumeBinding (volumebinding/volume_binding.go:491), ImageLocality (imagelocality/image_locality.go:73), TaintToleration (tainttoleration/taint_toleration.go:208), and BalancedAllocation (noderesources/balanced_allocation.go:112). Most return nil, while InterPodAffinity, PodTopologySpread, NodeAffinity, and TaintToleration return self (pl or ba).\n\nThe runtime framework file pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework.go calls ScoreExtensions() twice (lines 1171 and 1235) within the RunScoreExtensionPlugin function, which executes the NormalizeScore method of plugins that implement the ScoreExtensions interface. Line 1236 also references the metrics.ScoreExtensionNormalize constant.\n\nThe metrics file pkg/scheduler/metrics/metrics.go defines the ScoreExtensionNormalize constant (line 74) which tracks the duration of ScoreExtension normalization calls.\n\nTesting infrastructure includes fake plugins in pkg/scheduler/testing/framework/fake_plugins.go (FakePreScoreAndScorePlugin) and fake_extender.go (node2PrioritizerPlugin) that implement ScoreExtensions().\n\nTest files referencing ScoreExtensions include test/integration/scheduler/plugins/plugins_test.go (ScorePlugin and ScoreWithNormalizePlugin implementations), pkg/scheduler/schedule_one_test.go (falseMapPlugin, numericMapPlugin, reverseNumericMapPlugin), pkg/scheduler/framework/runtime/framework_test.go (TestScoreWithNormalizePlugin, TestScorePlugin, TestPlugin), and three plugin-specific test files that call ScoreExtensions().NormalizeScore(): interpodaffinity/scoring_test.go (lines 813, 976), nodeaffinity/node_affinity_test.go (line 1224), and tainttoleration/taint_toleration_test.go (line 261)."
